---
// Header.astro — Page header with site branding
---
<header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-700 dark:from-blue-800 dark:to-indigo-900 text-white py-12 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="text-5xl mb-4">⚡</div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-3 tracking-tight">CLI Tools Guide</h1>
    <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Master the command line. Practical guides, tips, and tricks for modern CLI tools like
      <code class="bg-blue-500/40 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-white font-mono text-base">bat</code>,
      <code class="bg-blue-500/40 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-white font-mono text-base">vim</code>,
      <code class="bg-blue-500/40 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-white font-mono text-base">fzf</code> and more.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>
